API, they can use bundled classes from 0.9. \\n\\nNow, if deterministic setup includes dependencies, I should prepare accordingly and make sure Sisu has Guice. The existing build.gradle already includes necessary dependencies, so I'll consider any edits to keep things organized.\"}]}"}, {"type": "text", "text": "{\n  \"action\": \"advisory_preparation\",\n  \"summary\": \"Sisu Inject is an in-process JSR-330/Guice integration library, so it does not need Docker or an external service. Its resolved POM marks Guice as provided, and lifecycle-oriented coverage on JDK 25 needs the Java EE annotation API explicitly.\",\n  \"deterministic_setup\": [\n    {\n      \"kind\": \"dependency\",\n      \"coordinate\": \"com.google.inject:guice:5.1.0\",\n      \"scope\": \"testImplementation\",\n      \"reason\": \"org.eclipse.sisu.inject compiles against Guice but declares it as provided; generated tests that exercise the public Sisu API need Guice classes on the test classpath.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"kind\": \"dependency\",\n      \"coordinate\": \"javax.annotation:javax.annotation-api:1.3.2\",\n      \"scope\": \"testImplementation\",\n      \"reason\": \"Sisu lifecycle support uses javax.annotation types such as PostConstruct and PreDestroy, which are not supplied by modern JDKs.\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"agent_guidance\": \"No external service is needed. Exercise Sisu with real Guice injectors/modules and update tests for the 0.9 API: MutableBeanLocator.add now accepts a BindingPublisher, so wrap an Injector with InjectorBindings rather than calling the removed add(Injector, int) overload.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"The artifact manifest lists optional OSGi, servlet, SLF4J, and test-framework packages; do not add those dependencies unless the generated tests intentionally cover those optional integrations.\",\n    \"Existing 0.3.5 tests may contain calls to Sisu APIs removed or narrowed in 0.9.0.M1, so javac failures are more likely API drift than missing infrastructure.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_06f4d26bdb392509016a277812fd848194afb7c82fd673e385\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 6190, "output": 1145, "cacheRead": 25088, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 32423, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1780971522482, "responseId": "resp_06f4d26bdb392509016a277802f74881948610975ec79e5cc3"}}
